    "caption": "We're in Utrecht for Christmas.\n\nWe're away from his boat and my cabin... But the hotel we're staying in is remarkably like being in one of those two. It has a sort of double bunk attached to the wall which you crawl onto and netting either side of the bed for possessions and a tiny bathroom compartment. It's quite fun.",
