    "id": "post_105",
    "images": [
      "17971115929823185.webp"
    ],
    "caption": "Home, sweet home. I liked this pic as it has a Edward Hopperesque quality \n\nMy new house has had builders gutting it for a couple of weeks now.  I imagine it will be a few months before I can live there. Hopefully we're close to the end of the destruction and demolition and heading back up soon.\n\nI'm feeling super ambivalent about the whole project and house right now, but hopefully my enthusiasm will come. On the other hand, maybe it will just encourage me to plan more adventures for those times when I'm not with the girls.",
