    "id": "post_117",
    "images": [
      "18250724839115144.webp"
    ],
    "caption": "Camping this last weekend was cold. Fortunately I had my silk sleeping bag liner, down bag, down quilt and a hot water bottle. On the one hand, perhaps all that was silly, but (a) I was warm at night (b) there was actually frost when I woke up. Frost in September.\n\nI stupidly signed up for another camping thing in February. So now I need more gear.",
