    "caption": "My friend Joe, who I met at another festival, asked me along to the one I just went to. I was a bit intimidated by the place, but he arrived the day after me threw up his tent and said \"ok let's go out on the trail\". I was worried as it has been nearly 15 years since I've ridden road, but he cajoled me into doing it and it was fun. Then the next day, I wasn't going to ride anything and he helped me blag a place on a Ducati ride out, then said he and another friend we're going to ride sportsbikes (which was totally new to me) so I went along and then we Rode the Africa Twin (Honda's big adventure bike) off road too. \n\nOn top of that, saw a load of great speakers and even rode a mechanical bull.\n\nHad a super fun weekend. Absolutely shattered, but way more excited for a week of work than if I'd had a weekend with the telly.",
