    "caption": "Super (un)healthy vegan 'Parks and Rec' breakfast. Though the vegan aspect would clearly offend Ron  to his core. I'm hoping Lesley would forgive me.\n\nA friend recently recommend @movingmountainsfoods Sausage and it's amazingly good. The kids asked me why I had made them meat sausages rather than vegan ones.\n\nThe bacon is Mheat, which is nor a bad approximation of maple bacon.\n\nAnd the waffles were made with my @sageappliancesuk waffle maker.\n\n#veganbreakfast #vegan",
