    "caption": "My parents came to visit this weekend, which has been very lovely. We went for a muddy, cold tramp through Stanmer park, followed by lunch in a cafe. To save everyone else getting cold, I offered to walk back to get the car. Robyn offered to walk back with me, which was a couple of miles up a muddy hill. It was such a lovely little interlude of intimacy between us as we stomped back to the car park. She babbled away, but was clearly revelling in the private moment. I feel very lucky to have her in my life.",
