    "caption": "I stayed up till three in the morning talking but had to get up at five to do physio before being picked up. I feel like death. Fortunately the lounge has a dim sum bar so I will be climbing my way out of this dark hole with the aid of many pork buns, dumplings and black coffee. If I evaluate this time in Thailand as essentially a business trip, it has definitely been a successful from an outcome basis, but I also met some wonderful and interesting people. That being said, I am very much looking forward to being home.",
