    "caption": "Last morning together before my long trip to Thailand. After a guilt fuelled day buying them Christmas grade presents and other treats, I woke up feeling very blue. I guess it's about many things: not seeing them for a month, about the weirdness of walking away from projects at work and of close friendships that I imagine will be changed as a cost of this. Not to mention how unprepared I suddenly feel.\n\nMy girls came into my bed and we ended up just cuddling and talking and giggling. \nThe Lego building has now resumed and both the Millennium Falcon and Princess Jasmine's Palace are taking shape on my kitchen table.\n\nSo much to do today. #last24hours",
